  section.sg-sect#inline-object
    h2 The Inline Object
    p.
      A simple inline object. Use this class to display an element as an
      inline element,
      with zero line-height to maintain vertical rhythm.
    p.
      This class is useful for creating inline lists, that is,
      lists whose items are each displayed one right after another, inline.
