  section.sg-sect#bare-list
    h2 The Bare List
    p.
      Use the Bare List object to remove the usual padding and list item markers accompanied by
      (un)ordered lists. The result is a list of items, each on its own line.
      Combine this class with other classes to create a variety of styles.
    figure.sg-c-Fig
