  section.sg-sect#stacked-list
    h2 The Stacked List
    p.
      The Stacked List Object is usually an unordered list (though it can be ordered) of blocky items.
      These items may be sponsor logos, passes, speakers, and more. This Object is responsive,
      adjusting its items&rsquo; widths at different breakpoints.
    figure.sg-c-Fig
      ul.o-ListBare.o-GridFlex.o-ListStacked
        each val in [1,2,3]
          li.o-GridFlex__Item.o-ListStacked__Item
            article
              h1 a blocky heading
              p blocky content
      pre.
        &lt;ul class="o-ListBare  o-GridFlex  #[u o-ListStacked]"&gt;
